## ğŸ“¦ Installation

### From PyPI
```bash
pip install nexus-lang
```

### From Source
```bash
git clone https://github.com/nexus-lang/nexus.git
cd nexus
pip install -e ".[dev]"
```

### VS Code Extension
```bash
cd vscode-nexus
npm install && npm run compile
code --install-extension nexus-lang-1.0.0.vsix
```

